# cargo-fuzz: build outputs are reproducible, coverage profiles are
# large. Seed corpus under fuzz/corpus/<target>/ IS tracked — once
# it grows past the seed set, minimize with `cargo fuzz cmin` and
# commit the trimmed result. `fuzz/artifacts/` holds reproducer
# inputs for discovered crashes; committing those is fine too, but
# our runs are currently clean.
fuzz/target/
fuzz/coverage/
